1097
01:20:12,345 --> 01:20:14,139
?No quieres una copa?

1098
01:20:16,850 --> 01:20:19,644
Ya veràs qué bien. Así.

1099
01:20:20,353 --> 01:20:22,689
- Es barro.
- !Si acabas de quitàrmelo!

1100
01:20:22,939 --> 01:20:25,191
Èste te darà un aspecto.

1101
01:20:26,067 --> 01:20:27,485
Es buen barro.

1102
01:20:30,155 --> 01:20:31,865
Cierra.

1103
01:20:32,532 --> 01:20:33,742
Los labios.

1104
01:20:37,996 --> 01:20:39,205
Cierra.

1105
01:20:39,414 --> 01:20:40,457
?Qué haces?

1106
01:20:42,375 --> 01:20:44,043
Eso es.

1107
01:20:44,836 --> 01:20:47,380
Ahora relàjate.

1108
01:20:49,883 --> 01:20:52,093
?Hay alguien
especial en tu vida?

1109
01:20:52,677 --> 01:20:55,555
